<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="safety-n">safety <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'seɪfti/    美 /'seɪfti/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>安全：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>road safety</strong> 
道路安全</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ensure the safety 
确保安全</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They crossed the road <strong>in safety</strong>. 
他们安全地穿过了马路。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>For your own <strong><em>_</em></strong> (安全), please keep away from the tiger cage.  （2015 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. safety  </p></div>